snippet.title: Johnny Depp threatens to ‘BURN’ and ‘DROWN’ ex-wife Amber Heard!? TEXTS RESURFACING!?
snippet.description:
Oh brother.. Amber is pretty desperate NOW... I’ll Link my sources below! What’re your guys thoughts? Saying something and ACTUALLY doing it are two different things... I’m NOT saying “treats” are okay but I feel like these things were said in jest nothing serious.... 🤯😬 I mean if he was really going to do those things I’m sure we’d know by now. Damn. 

My first video on the topic: 

https://youtu.be/MFg1TVAv5TA
🤯 

⚠️ ⚠️ https://pagesix.com/2020/02/26/court-hears-johnny-depps-texts-threatening-to-burn-ex-wife-amber-heard/


https://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=12312087


https://www.scmp.com/news/world/europe/article/3052565/johnny-depp-sues-over-wife-beater-article-british-tabloid-sun. 

The link directly above is about Johnny Suing the Sun tabloid
